{"descriptions":[{"id":457,"title":"Destruction Ritual","content":"\u003ch1\u003eDescription\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDestruction rituals involve violent or fierce action (darg po'i las), sometimes for religious ends, but often to bring harm to or to kill an enemy.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch1\u003eRelated Terms\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 10px;\"\u003emngon spyod kyi las (wrathful magic) = abhicāra; \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 10px;\"\u003edrag po'i las (wrathful ritual); \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 10px;\"\u003ehom, hom gyi las (hom-pit rituals); \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 10px;\"\u003ekhrag sbyor (blood practice); \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 10px;\"\u003elas mtha' (extreme rituals)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch1\u003eExample Texts\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003emngon spyod kyi las (Toh. 484)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"http://tbrc.org/#!rid=W15723\"\u003edrag sngags mngon spyod kyi rnam bzhag\u003c/a\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"http://tbrc.org/#!rid=W5422\"\u003erdo rje legs pa'i las mtha' gnam lcags thog chen\u003c/a\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"http://tbrc.org/#!rid=W10947\"\u003erten 'brel snying po'i drag po'i las byang\u003c/a\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"http://tbrc.org/#!rid=W15722\"\u003edrag po'i las bskul ba\u003c/a\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"http://tbrc.org/#!rid=W15825\"\u003etsi'u dmar po'i phrin las\u003c/a\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch1\u003eSecondary Sources\u003c/h1\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003c!--[if gte mso 9]\u003e\u003cxml\u003e Normal   0         false   false   false               